last_episode_to_air.name: Episode 30
last_episode_to_air.overview: Radwan takes pictures of Fathy murdering Fadwa and Yasser.  Abir's daughter dies. Hamada and Noura rekindle their love and get married. Radwan forces Fathy to sign a check, giving him his inheritance. Abdel Mohsen commits suicide, and Fathy is sentenced to death. Radwan marries Ola.

name: The Prince
overview: A social drama that chronicles the life of Al-Prince family, especially Radwan Al-Prince who, following the death of his parents, finds himself involved with his family members as he looks after them and tries to guide them through life.
